Package: gridPoints
Type: Package
Title: Functions for gridding point data
Version: 0.21
Date: 2016-05-27
Author: Robin Edward
Maintainer: Robin Edwards <geotheory1@gmail.com>
Description: Package offers 3 functions to grid point data.  grid_points() is a flexible data aggregator.  grid_jitter() and grid_jitter2() deterministically adjust point positions to prevent over-plotting (see help pages for more detail).
License: GPL-2
Imports:
    ggplot2,
    plyr,
    gridExtra,
    clue